message.content: cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.CV. The paper discusses the development of a neural network architecture with external memory, which is a common topic in the fields of neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) as it uses the bAbI dataset for testing. Additionally, the architecture involves image processing (cs.CV) as it is capable of finding the shortest path between nodes in a path.
